<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1303709>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–9. 1, 4, 7 Siniassus hamulus sp. nov.; 2, 5, 8. Decliviassus sagittatus sp. nov.; 3, 6, 9. Krisna quadrimaculosus sp. nov.; 1–3. Dorsal view; 4–6. Lateral view; 7–9. Facial view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1303709/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1303719>
    dc:description "FIGURES 43–65. Krisna species. 43. K. expansiva (Li & Wang), connective ventral view; 44–45. K. rufimarginata (Cai & He), pygofer ventral process, ventral view; 46. K. daiyunensis (Cai & He), apex of aedeagus, caudal view; 47. K. daiyunensis (Cai & He), pygofer ventral process, ventral view; 48. K. viraktamathi (Zhang & Dai), pygofer ventral process, ventral view; 49. K. furcata (Zhang & Dai), pygofer ventral process, ventral view; 50. K. viridula (Li & Wang), pygofer ventral process, ventral view; 51. K. daiyunensis (Zhang & Dai), aedeagus, lateral view; 52. K. furcata (Zhang & Dai), aedeagus, lateral view; 53. K. viridula (Li & Wang), aedeagus, lateral view; 54. K. viraktamathi (Zhang & Dai), aedeagus, lateral view; 55. K. concava (Li & Wang), aedeagus, lateral view; 56. K. yingjiangensis (Li & Wang), aedeagus, lateral view; 57. K. furcata (Zhang & Dai), aedeagus, caudal view; 58. K. expansive (Li & Wang), aedeagus, ventral view; 59. K. daiyunensis (Zhang & Dai), male eighth sternite, ventral view; 60. K. expansive (Li & Wang), male eighth sternite, ventral view; 61. K. yingjiangensis (Li & Wang), male eighth sternite, ventral view; 62. K. concava (Li & Wang), male eighth sternite, ventral view; 63. K. nigromarginata (Cai & He), pygophore, lateral view; 64. K. expansive (Li & Wang), pygophore, lateral view; 65. K. yingjiangensis (Li & Wang), pygophore, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1303719/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1303715>
    dc:description "FIGURES 30–36. Decliviassus species. 30. D bipunctatus (Dai, Dietrich & Zhang), apex of aedeagus, ventral view; 31. D. bipunctatus (Dai, Dietrich & Zhang), aedeagus, lateral view; 32. D. maculatus (Dai, Dietrich & Zhang), style, lateral view; 33. D. nudus (Dai, Dietrich & Zhang), style, lateral view; 34. D. nudus (Dai, Dietrich & Zhang), aedeagus, lateral view; D. nudus (Dai, Dietrich & Zhang), aedeagus, ventral view; 36. D. bipunctatus (Dai, Dietrich & Zhang), aedeagus, style and connective, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1303715/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1303711>
    dc:description "FIGURES 10–25. Siniassus species. 10. S. loberus (Dai, Zhang & Zhang), subgenital plate; 11. S. aspinus (Dai, Zhang & Zhang), subgenital plate, ventral view; 12. S. compressus (Dai, Zhang & Zhang), subgenital plate, ventral view; 13. S. webbi (Dai & Dietrich), subgenital plate, ventral view; 14. S. webbi (Dai & Dietrich), style; 15. S. webbi (Dai & Dietrich), magnified view of apex of aedeagal shaft, caudal view; 16. S. webbi (Dai & Dietrich), aedeagus, lateral view; 17. S. compressus (Dai, Zhang & Zhang), aedeagus, lateral view; 18. S. compressus (Dai, Zhang & Zhang), aedeagus, ventral view; 19. S. aspinus (Dai, Zhang & Zhang), aedeagus, lateral view; 20. S. aspinus (Dai, Zhang & Zhang), aedeagus, ventral view; 21. S. loberus (Dai, Zhang & Zhang), Male pygofer, lateral view; 22. S. loberus (Dai, Zhang & Zhang), male pygofer, caudal view; 23. S. aspinus (Dai, Zhang & Zhang), male pygofer, lateral view; 24. S. compressus (Dai, Zhang & Zhang), male pygofer, lateral view; 25. S. webbi (Dai & Dietrich), male pygofer, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1303711/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

